OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPoundland owner to take on 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fup to 71 Wilko stores      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The owner of Poundland has agreed to   
OL,6, take on the leases of dozens of Wilko  
OL,7, shops.                                 
OL,9,FPepco Group, which owns Poundland in   
OL,10,Fthe UK, is expected to convert up to 71
OL,11,FWilko stores to the Poundland brand.   
OL,13,FPoundland boss Barry Williams said it  
OL,14,Frecognised the last few weeks had been 
OL,15,Fdifficult for Wilko workers.           
OL,17,FIn a statement, the company said that  
OL,18,FWilko staff would have priority when   
OL,19,Fapplying for new jobs at the Poundland 
OL,20,Fshops.                                 
